print.simulation

Class List

  • java.lang.Object
    • print.simulation.List
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Queue

    public class List
extends java.lang.Object
    List.java A class that creates a List to be used as a stack, queue, or otherwise. With methods to insert and remove Objects as nodes from either the back or the front of the list. 
        Project: print.simulation
    Platform: jdk 1.6.0_14; NetBeans IDE 6.8; Mac OSx
    Course: CS 143
    Hours: 2 hours
    Created on May 25th, 2013, 10:00:00 PM
    See Also:
    PrintSimulationGUI, Queue, ListNode

        public void insertAtBack(java.lang.Object insertItem)
